M83                      ; use relative distances for extrusion 
G28                      ; home all axes (X,Y,Z) 
G21                      ; set units to millimeters 
G1 X30 Y185 Z5 F3600     ; put nozzle in this position before heating process 
G90                      ; absolute position for XYZ axes 
M140 S90                 ; start heating the bed to 90 degrees Celsius 
M190 S90                 ; wait until the bed reaches 90 degrees before continuing 
M104 S190 T0              ; start heating T0 to 200 degrees Celsius 
M109 S190 T0              ; wait until T0 to reach 200 degrees before continuing  

